<section class="section">
    <header class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-title">How Softprobe AI SRE Works</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 01</div>
            <h3 class="step-label">Capture & Replay</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">
                Softprobe silently captures real production traffic and user sessions. Before your next release, our AI replays them in your test environment to validate everything works.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 02</div>
            <h3 class="step-label">Softprobe Builds the Session Graph</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">
                Every request, response, and execution path is stored as a structured session graph â€” 100% of data, zero sampling. This gives AI a complete map of your system behavior.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-num">STEP 03</div>
            <h3 class="step-label">AI SRE handles testing, production monitoring and debugging</h3>
            <p class="step-desc">
                Structured session graph architecture enables agentic review of execution path to find exact error causes; fully deterministic (no probabilistic guessing).
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section {
        width: 100%;
        padding: var(--site-page-padding-desktop);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 60px;
    }

    .section-head {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 880px;
    }

    .section-title {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4.2vw, 3.2rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #111827;
    }

    .steps-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 24px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: var(--site-max-width);
    }

    .step-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 32px;
        box-shadow: 
            0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05),
            0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .step-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 
            0 10px 15px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05),
            0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .step-num {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #3b82f6;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .step-label {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.2;
        color: #111827;
    }

    .step-desc {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4b5563;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
        .steps-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
    }
</style>
